Privacy Policy for MiAmor Chat and Date
Effective Date: May 12, 2025

MiAmor Chat and Date ("MiAmor", "we", "us", or "our") respects your privacy and is committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, store, and disclose your information when you use our mobile application (the "App").

By registering for or using the MiAmor app, you agree to the terms outlined in this Privacy Policy.

1. Information We Collect
When you register and use MiAmor Chat and Date, we collect the following types of information:

1.1. Information You Provide
Personal Identification Information: Name, Age, Town, Country

Contact Information: Email address and Phone number (kept private by default)

Personal Interests: Hobbies and interests

Photos: Up to 3 user-uploaded profile photos

Account Credentials: Email and password (encrypted)

1.2. Usage Data
Chat interactions with other users

Contact requests and responses (accepted or denied)

App preferences and settings

Log files (e.g., IP address, device type, timestamps)

1.3. Device & Technical Data
Device model and operating system

App version

Advertising identifiers (used for ad services and analytics)

2. How We Use Your Information
We use your information to:

Create and manage your MiAmor account

Display your public profile (excluding private contact details)

Enable chat and interactive features within the app

Facilitate user-to-user contact requests (with your consent)

Provide user support and respond to inquiries

Improve the app‚Äôs performance and user experience

Serve personalized ads to support app development and maintenance

Monitor and enforce community and legal standards

3. Sharing Your Information
3.1. With Other Users
Publicly visible: Name, Age, Town, Country, Interests, Hobbies, Profile Photos

Private by default: Your Email and Phone Number will only be shared with users if you explicitly grant them access

3.2. With Third Parties
We may share non-sensitive information with:

Ad Networks (e.g., Google AdMob) for displaying ads

Analytics Providers to understand usage trends and optimize features

Service Providers (e.g., hosting, cloud services) necessary for the operation of the app

We never sell your personal data to third parties.

4. User Controls and Choices
You have full control over your data and privacy preferences:

Edit Profile: Update your displayed information and settings at any time

Control Contact Sharing: Accept or deny contact info requests from other users

Account Deletion: Delete your account from within the app or request deletion via email

Profile Visibility: Manage how your information is displayed and shared

5. Data Security
We take your data security seriously:

All sensitive data is encrypted during transmission and storage

Passwords are securely hashed and never stored in plain text

Access to your data is restricted to authorized personnel only

Despite our efforts, no system is completely secure. You use the app at your own discretion.

6. Data Retention
We retain your data as long as your account is active

Upon deletion, your personal information and photos are removed from our systems within 30 days

Some minimal information may be kept temporarily for fraud prevention or legal compliance

7. Children's Privacy
This app is strictly for users aged 18 years or older. We do not knowingly collect data from minors. If underage use is discovered, the associated account will be removed immediately.

8. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices or legal obligations. You will be notified of major changes via the app or email. Continued use after updates implies acceptance.

9. Contact Us
For any questions, concerns, or privacy-related requests, please contact us at:

